-- MOVES-RBC Wealth Management names financial adviser to Scottsdale office
-- 
-- Tue Sep 16, 2014 01:39AM EDT
-- None



Sept 16 (Reuters) - RBC Wealth Management, a securities firm, appointed Charles Pisoni financial adviser to its Scottsdale office.

Pisoni joins RBC Wealth Management from Merrill Lynch and has assets under management of more than $250 million and $1.5 million in production.   RBC also appointed Debbie Papa senior client associate.